UID:propiq-cancel-intercom@propiq.luntra.one
SUMMARY:🚨 CANCEL INTERCOM SUBSCRIPTION
DESCRIPTION:CRITICAL ACTION REQUIRED: Cancel Intercom to avoid $888/year charge\n\n**Renewal Date:** October 28\, 2026 (7 days from now)\n**Cost if not canceled:** $74/month = $888/year\n**Savings:** $888/year by canceling\n\n**Why Cancel:**\n✅ You have custom AI support chat built\n✅ No need for Intercom anymore\n✅ Save $888/year\n\n**Cancellation Steps:**\n1. Login to Intercom: https://app.intercom.com\n2. Go to Settings → Subscription\n3. Click "Cancel subscription"\n4. Select reason: "No longer need this service"\n5. Confirm cancellation\n6. Screenshot confirmation page\n7. Verify end date is Oct 28\, 2026\n8. Save confirmation email\n\n**Post-Cancellation:**\n• Remove INTERCOM_ACCESS_TOKEN from backend/.env\n• Remove INTERCOM_API_KEY from backend/.env\n• Update backend/routers/intercom.py (mark as deprecated)\n• Document cancellation in SERVICE_SUBSCRIPTIONS_TRACKER.md\n\n**Verify on Oct 28:** Check bank/credit card - no charge from Intercom\n\n**Next step:** Remove Intercom code from codebase (Nov 1)
LOCATION:https://app.intercom.com/a/apps/_/settings/subscription
